metadata.name: Birthday Suits
metadata.description:
Made in SF x Open Edition

After years of visiting SF through my photo journey I find nothing holds a visual signature of San Francisco quite like walking nude on Baker beach. As one of the few nude beaches around the city this place is an iconic place for locals and visitors alike.

Made in San Francisco - A photo documentary of San Francisco culture shaped by its unique districts. This project was shot over 2 years and over 100 rolls of film slowly showcasing the city and how the history changed and visually developed these areas.

Shot on

Mamiya 645e  
Cinestill 800t
